name: Pirate Tricorn Hat Duck card
description:
I love to collect cards! Do you like it too?

This is the third of a series of digital collectible cards (inspired by the old baseball ones), featuring this (this time not so) sweet and kind looking duck wearing all sorts of hats.
 
This time it's a pirate tricorn hat!

At total it'll be 10 different cards with different rarities.
